---

This is a compatibility add-on and interoperates with three separate mods.
It does not bundle their code. Small derived assets and attribution:

- Armored Elytra (https://github.com/DorkixAzIgazi/armored-elytra) — MIT.
  This mod extends Armored Elytra's icon system and reuses its trim template
  at runtime; derived icon models are used under the MIT License.
- Enderite Mod (https://github.com/Nic4Las/Minecraft-Enderite-Mod) — MIT.
  Icon models/textures derived from the enderite elytra and chestplate are
  used under the MIT License.
- Elytra Trims (https://codeberg.org/KikuGie/elytra-trims) — LGPL-3.0.
  Used as an optional runtime dependency only; no Elytra Trims code or assets
  are redistributed.
